## 7. Update `UserService`

Inject:

```java
private final SalesPointRepository salesPointRepository;
private final PersonSalesPointRelationshipRepository relationshipRepository;
```

Then inside `mapToResponse()`:

```java
List<SalesPointResponse> salesPoints =
        relationshipRepository.findByPersonUserId(user.getUserId())
                .stream()
                .map(rel -> {
                    SalesPointEntity salesPoint = salesPointRepository
                            .findBySalesPointId(rel.getSalesPointId())
                            .orElseThrow(() -> new IllegalArgumentException(
                                    "Sales point not found: " + rel.getSalesPointId()
                            ));

                    return new SalesPointResponse(
                            salesPoint.getSalesPointId(),
                            salesPoint.getLabel(),
                            rel.getOrgUnitId(),
                            rel.getRelationshipType()
                    );
                })
                .toList();

response.setSalesPoints(salesPoints);
```

